                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940917-107-defend1347 t17940917-107-punish557"></join>
               Privately whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
